item.title: ANA @ BUF
item.description: This post will take a look at the box score in Visualization form. The goal of this post is to quickly view who scored and assisted on goals from the game. Buffalo Sabres: 3 (Win) Once again, the top line strikes, with both Jack Eichel and Sam Reinhart provding to assists on the night and Jeff Skinner scoring another goal. Anaheim Ducks: 0 (Loss)
